<li>"<a href="/wiki/The_Beast_that_Shouted_Love_at_the_Heart_of_the_World_(short_story)" title="The Beast that Shouted Love at the Heart of the World (short story)">The Beast that Shouted Love at the Heart of the World</a>"</li>
