<li>"<a href="/wiki/I_Have_No_Mouth,_and_I_Must_Scream" title="I Have No Mouth, and I Must Scream">I Have No Mouth, and I Must Scream</a>" Made into <a href="/wiki/CD-ROM" title="CD-ROM">CD-ROM</a> Game, circa 1995-97</li>
