<p><a name="Documentary_film" id="Documentary_film"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Harlan_Ellison&amp;action=edit&amp;section=39" title="Edit section: Documentary film">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Documentary film</span></h3>
<ul>
<li>Erik Nelson (writer and director). <i>Dreams with Sharp Teeth</i> (made 2002-2007, released 2008). A documentary film about Ellison's life and work.</li>
</ul>
